Insider Activity


Individual




Gregory T. Barmore



Mr. Gregory T. Barmore is Independent Director at A. Schulman, Inc. and President at Holbrook Community Foundation. He is on the Board of Directors at A. Schulman, Inc., Bennett College, Maine Maritime Museum, Maine Island Trail Association, Harbor Technologies LLC, and Therma-HEXX Corp.
Mr. Barmore was previously employed as Chairman by ICO, Inc., Chairman by ICO Polymers, Inc., Lead Independent Director by Novation Cos., Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by GE Capital Mortgage, Chief Financial Officer by Employers Reinsurance Corp., a Member-Governors Board by Mortgage Bankers Association, President by Consumer Mortgage Coalition, and President by Mortgage Insurance Companies of America.
He received his undergraduate degree from Tufts University.



